} into {{another place}}. Fast motion, motion blur. In the style of {{describe style; ex. hyperlapse cinematography}}."}},{id:"close-up-portrait",name:"Close-up portrait",taskType:"gen3a",settings:{textPrompt:"A crash zoom into a close-up portrait, shallow depth of field, bokeh. In the style of {{describe style; ex. muted color palette, neutrals, magic hour, dull, dramatic, moody, film, 35mm}}."}},{id:"low-angle",name:"Low angle",taskType:"gen3a",settings:{textPrompt:"Low angle shot: A {{subject ex. car}} drives down the center of a {{place ex. city}}. Tall {{objects ex. buildings}} loom on either side, their {{objects ex. windows}} blurred in the background."}},{id:"high-angle",name:"High angle",taskType:"gen3a",settings:{textPrompt:"Aerial tracking shot: glide over {{place}}. Camera Movement: Start high, descend closer to {{place}}."}},{id:"first-person-view",name:"First person view",taskType:"gen3a",settings:{textPrompt:"First person view shot flying through {{objects ex. canyons}} of a {{place ex. planet}} toward a {{object ex. moon}}."}},{id:"handheld",name:"Handheld",taskType:"gen3a",settings:{textPrompt:"Handheld tracking shot, following a {{subject}} in a {{place}}."}},{id:"close-up",name:"Close up",taskType:"gen3a",settings:{textPrompt:"Telephoto close up: {{subject}}."}},{id:"macro-cinematography",name:"Macro cinematography",taskType:"gen3a",settings:{textPrompt:"Macro cinematography: A large {{object ex. water droplet}} rests among {{objects ex. succulent plants}}. The {{object}} refracts and distorts the view of the surrounding environment. Camera Movement: Start with a close-up of the {{object}}, then slowly pull back to reveal more of the surreal {{plant life}}."}},{id:"over-the-shoulder",name:"Over the shoulder",taskType:"gen3a",settings:{textPrompt:"Over the shoulder shot: {{subject doing X}}. The camera trails behind them."}},{id:"establishing-wide",name:"Establishing wide",taskType:"gen3a",settings:{textPrompt:"Extreme wide angle establishing shot: {{subject}} in vast {{scene}}."}},{id:"dynamic-motion",name:"Dynamic motion",taskType:"gen3a",settings:{textPrompt:"Dynamic motion, dynamic blur, 30x speed, unsharp edges."}},{id:"slow-motion",name:"Slow motion",taskType:"gen3a",settings:{textPrompt:"Slow motion shot: {{a subject in motion}}."}},{id:"fast-zoom",name:"Fast zoom",taskType:"gen3a",settings:{textPrompt:"Hyperspeed shot: {{scene}}. Camera movement: fast zoom."}},{id:"fast-motion",name:"Fast motion",taskType:"gen3a",settings:{textPrompt:"High speed, motion blur, chaotic, kinetic, hyperkinetic."}},{id:"static-camera",name:"Static camera",taskType:"gen3a",settings:{textPrompt:"Static camera. The camera is still."}}],i=new Set(n.map(e=>e.panel)),o=[{id:"claymation",name:"Claymation",taskType:"gen3a",settings:{textPrompt:"Clay composition, matte clay textures with no reflection, claymation animation of {{your prompt here}} in the style of artistic clay animation, malformed clay with fingerprints, clay textures, colorful matte clay, imperfect clay formations, subject entirely made of clay.",structureTransformation:.8}},{id:"line-art",name:"Line Art",taskType:"gen3a",settings:{textPrompt:"Hand illustrated cartoon sketch style, natural color palette, {{your prompt here}} in the style of hand drawn animation with bold outlines and exaggerated features. Expressive, professional illustrated line art.",structureTransformation:.8}},{id:"3d-cartoon",name:"3D Cartoon",taskType:"gen3a",settings:{textPrompt:"3D cartoon, professionally rendered with volumetric lighting and shadows, {{your prompt here}} in the style of professional 3D render, expressive features, 3D ray traced lighting and shadows, high fidelity 3D cartoon render.",structureTransformation:.65}},{id:"monochrome",name:"Monochrome",taskType:"gen3a",settings:{textPrompt:"Monochrome color palette, black and white with high contrast shadows and lighting, {{your prompt here}} in the style of vintage black and white video, film grain, dramatic single point lighti