adows, bright highlights, intense details, cinematic look, bold tones"}},{id:"high-contrast-warm",name:"High Contrast Warm",previewUrl:`${r.yI}app/frames/style/compressed/high-contrast-warm.jpg`,taskType:"text_to_image",settings:{textPrompt:"high contrast, deep shadows, warm color grading, golden highlights, moody atmosphere, cinematic look"}},{id:"high-contrast-cool",name:"High Contrast Cool",previewUrl:`${r.yI}app/frames/style/compressed/high-contrast-cool.jpg`,taskType:"text_to_image",settings:{textPrompt:"high contrast, deep shadows, cool tones, steel blue highlights, moody atmosphere, cinematic look"}},{id:"bw",name:"B&W",previewUrl:`${r.yI}app/frames/style/compressed/bw.jpg`,taskType:"text_to_image",settings:{textPrompt:"black and white photography, balanced contrast, rich grayscale tones, clear details, classic look"}},{id:"bw-contrast",name:"B&W Contrast",previewUrl:`${r.yI}app/frames/style/compressed/bw-contrast.jpg`,taskType:"text_to_image",settings:{textPrompt:"high contrast black and white, deep blacks, bright highlights, film noir style, dramatic shadows"}},{id:"muted-pastel",name:"Muted Pastel",previewUrl:`${r.yI}app/frames/style/compressed/muted-pastel.jpg`,taskType:"text_to_image",settings:{textPrompt:"medium grain film texture, muted pastel colors, creamy highlights, lifted shadows, subtle teal in shadows, decreased contrast, elegant skin rendering"}},{id:"dreamscape",name:"Dreamscape",previewUrl:`${r.yI}app/frames/style/compressed/dreamscape.jpg`,taskType:"text_to_image",settings:{textPrompt:"teal tones, creamy whites, enhanced greens, lifted shadows, reduced highlights, soft dappled light, hazy glow, subtle brown undertones, dreamy atmosphere"}},{id:"nordic-minimal",name:"Nordic Minimal",previewUrl:`${r.yI}app/frames/style/compressed/nordic-minimal.jpg`,taskType:"text_to_image",settings:{textPrompt:"desaturated greens, slate blue undertones, bright whites, moody shadows, foggy atmosphere, matte blacks, cool temperature, ethereal highlights, minimalist contrast, milky sky tones"}},{id:"light-anime",name:"Light Anime",previewUrl:`${r.yI}app/frames/style/compressed/light-anime.jpg`,taskType:"text_to_image",settings:{textPrompt:"anime-style illustration. the scene is Japanese, slightly shallow depth of field. the lighting is bright and even, creating subtle shadows while maintaining the characteristic flat shading style common in anime artwork"}},{id:"dark-anime",name:"Dark Anime",previewUrl:`${r.yI}app/frames/style/compressed/dark-anime.jpg`,taskType:"text_to_image",settings:{textPrompt:"dark anime-style illustration. dark, shadowy Japanese backdrop that is slightly blurry. the anime color palette consists of muted golds and browns, deep crimson, and dark greys and blacks with subtle touches of blue-green in the ambient shadows"}},{id:"painted-anime",name:"Painted Anime",previewUrl:`${r.yI}app/frames/style/compressed/painted-anime.jpg`,taskType:"text_to_image",settings:{textPrompt:"Japanese anime, soft watercolor textures, pastel color palette, hand-painted backgrounds, gentle light diffusion, whimsical atmosphere, naturalistic lighting, detailed environmental elements, flowing organic shapes, subtle color gradients, dreamy depth of field"}},{id:"3d-cartoon",name:"3D Cartoon",previewUrl:`${r.yI}app/frames/style/compressed/3d-cartoon.jpg`,taskType:"text_to_image",settings:{textPrompt:"3D animation, a semi-realistic art style that balances cartoonish exaggeration with realistic details in proportions, volumetric lighting, smooth 3D forms, ambient occlusion, glow, soft colors, subtle orange undertones, and bounce lighting enhancing mood and depth. intricate in background scenery and details, with a depth of field"}},{id:"sketch",name:"Sketch",previewUrl:`${r.yI}app/frames/style/compressed/sketch.jpg`,taskType:"text_to_image",settings:{textPrompt:"rough pencil sketches, gestural line work, high contrast shading, composition guides, dynamic perspective lines, minimal color notes, loose brushwork, emphasis on movement, quick render style, storytelling angles"}},{id:"low-angle",name:"Low Angle",previewUrl:`${r.yI}app/frames/style/compressed/low-angle.jpg`,taskType:"text_to_image",settings:{textPrompt:"photographed from an extreme camera angle, photographed from the ground looking up. grand perspective looking up with epic cinematic scale, the sky filling the top 2/3 of the frame. subject in clear focus with the background blurred from shallow depth of field. natural muted color palette with visible film grain and dark shadows"}},{id:"in-motion",name:"In Motion",previewUrl:`${r.yI}app/frames/style/compressed/in-motion.jpg`,taskType:"text_to_image",settings:{textPrompt:"dynamic 1980s album art, in motion, extremely blurred by camera movement, visually striking and uniquely dynamic composition with accent primary color for focused visual interest. minimal background to give foreground element more focus. this is a handheld wide shot taken with a 35mm lens with slow shutter speed, film, soft muted color story"}},{id:"terracotta",name:"Terracotta",previewUrl:`${r.yI}app/frames/style/compressed/terracotta.jpg`,taskType:"text_to_image",settings:{textPrompt:"sleek minimal campaign photography, realistic environment, organic shapes and textures, detailed, flat terra cotta brown color background, creating a grand experience with dynamic and award winning cinematic composition"}}];r.yI,r.yI,r.yI,r.yI,r.yI,r.yI,r.yI;let T={textPrompt:"",style:null,imagePrompt:null,imageReferenceSelection:[],cfgScale:null,steps:null,negativePrompt:"",systemPrompt:"",enhancePrompt:!0,imageCount:m.paid,resolution:h.paid}},80269:function(e,t,a){"use strict";a.d(t,{c:()=>o});var r=a(42727),n=a(25944),i=a(49174);let o=({withModality:e=!1,taskType:t})=>{let a=t===r.Cw?n.Dp:"ref_image_to_image_turbo"===t?i.s2:i.wS;return e?`${a} Image`:a}},63206:function(e,t,a){"use strict";a.d(t,{t:()=>o});var r=a(64100),n=a(82204);let i={items:[],pendingCount:{remaining:0,added:0}},o=(0,r.Ue)((e,t)=>({...i,add:a=>{let r=t().items